  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>What would you do if your refuge was no longer safe?</strong></i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the dilemma faced by Robertha in My Home(Minha Casa). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this point'n'click personal horror adventure, you will step into the shoes of Robertha. A college freshman going through a time of change in her life. Awakened at the crack of dawn by her anxiety and fear for the future, she decides to drink some water to refresh her thoughts and get back to sleep, but what seemed like a simple trip turns into an oppressive night where she must face not only her own fears, but something darker as well.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027470/extras/e89ff4feafbb4cf5045d9fd7ee1c4be3.poster.avif?t=1731512641\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027470/extras/e89ff4feafbb4cf5045d9fd7ee1c4be3.webm?t=1731512641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027470/extras/e89ff4feafbb4cf5045d9fd7ee1c4be3.mp4?t=1731512641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition, My House has:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A captivating original soundtrack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro graphics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An electrifying yet heartwarming story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027470/extras/6067ba1d335283f8aea12e1ea1a499fd.avif?t=1731512641\" width=616 height=400 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>What would you do if your refuge was no longer safe?</strong></i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the dilemma faced by Robertha in My Home(Minha Casa). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this point'n'click personal horror adventure, you will step into the shoes of Robertha. A college freshman going through a time of change in her life. Awakened at the crack of dawn by her anxiety and fear for the future, she decides to drink some water to refresh her thoughts and get back to sleep, but what seemed like a simple trip turns into an oppressive night where she must face not only her own fears, but something darker as well.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027470/extras/e89ff4feafbb4cf5045d9fd7ee1c4be3.poster.avif?t=1731512641\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027470/extras/e89ff4feafbb4cf5045d9fd7ee1c4be3.webm?t=1731512641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027470/extras/e89ff4feafbb4cf5045d9fd7ee1c4be3.mp4?t=1731512641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition, My House has:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A captivating original soundtrack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro graphics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An electrifying yet heartwarming story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027470/extras/6067ba1d335283f8aea12e1ea1a499fd.avif?t=1731512641\" width=616 height=400 /></span></p>",
